{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fdf0dab504","title":"接见空军党委会全体同志时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c56e1a15d2","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"fdf0dab504","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"林彪","id":"cce608ea44","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dace3fd921","type":"title","text":"接见空军党委会全体同志时的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"18376d8d3b","type":"paragraph","text":"一，无产阶级文化大革命形势大好，要坚信不移。会有曲折，会有反复，大联合了，还可能有分裂，不要怕。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90490f3e58","type":"paragraph","text":"二，不要怕乱，乱透了就好。乱的过程，对于每一个人都是斗私批修的过程。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a84f78ca32","type":"paragraph","text":"三，不要急，天塌不下来。天塌下来了，有我们伟大的领袖毛主席，有战无不胜的毛泽东思想。也可以撑过来，也可填平。反映情况要四快一慢。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1cefb9de44","type":"paragraph","text":"四， 要看主流，不要看支流。要调查研究，不要把话说死，不要打包票，有的组织大方向对，政策策略不对，也会失败，南昌起义就是这样。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"507717e213","type":"paragraph","text":"五，要心明眼亮，看清敌人，但不要夸大敌人，要相信群众大多数。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05ea038334","type":"paragraph","text":"六，支左就是支持毛泽东思想，支左不支派，符合毛泽东思想就支持，不符合毛泽东思想就不支持。支左不要搞小动作，不要支持一派打击一派。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffa8b3ae9f","type":"paragraph","text":"七，反映情况要准，不要虚构，要全面，要客观。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d91ff8fce6","type":"paragraph","text":"八，争取主动，不要怕吃眼前亏，有错误 要认真检查，从根本上改造世界观。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b70c27a30b","type":"paragraph","text":"九，既要防“左”，又要防右。防“左”就是防干扰毛泽东思想，防干扰毛主席最新指示，坚决站在毛主席一边，防右就是防老保翻天。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fdf0dab504","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}